 and achieve extremely fast convergence to\nnear-optimal fugacities, and often outperform the convergence rate of the\nstochastic gradient descent by a few orders of magnitude.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jan 2016 16:38:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Feb 2017 13:08:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-24"}
