lem and the consensus problem. We show that for tree networks, the rate\nallocation results have a mathematical structure similar to classical reverse\nwater-filling for parallel Gaussian sources.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Jan 2016 03:39:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 13 Jan 2017 02:12:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-01-16"}
